Tau is a client living in Falador and is involved in the Mahogany Homes activity. She is one of the possible NPCs that the player can be tasked with helping.

Construction contracts[edit | edit source]

Tau is a possible client given to the player by Mahogany Homes, and may ask you to build the following furniture for them, depending on the type of contract that player chose:
